<section class="section">
  <div class="content-block">
    <h2>Our Mission</h2>
    <p>The Grande Ronde Association for Youth (G.R.A.Y.) was formed on {{ site.founded }} as a coalition of local youth sports organizations. Our mission is to facilitate the acquisition and improvement of sporting facilities in the Grande Ronde Valley of Oregon.</p>

    <h2>Who We Represent</h2>
    <p>G.R.A.Y. is a coalition representing the following youth sports organizations in Union County:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>La Grande Little League</li>
      <li>Union County Little League</li>
      <li>Babe Ruth Baseball</li>
      <li>Legion Baseball</li>
      <li>ASA Softball</li>
      <li>Union County Youth Soccer</li>
      <li>AAU Basketball</li>
      <li>Optimist Football</li>
      <li>Union County School Districts Athletics</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Our Accomplishments</h2>
    <p>Over the years, G.R.A.Y. has completed several significant community projects to improve youth sporting facilities in the valley:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Acquisition of Riveria School and Gym for the Riveria Activity Center</li>
      <li>Safety improvements to Imbler School Field</li>
      <li>Site preparation for baseball and soccer fields at Pioneer Park</li>
      <li>Acquisition of a top dressing machine for all fields in the valley</li>
      <li>Assistance to the field at the Union Sports Complex</li>
      <li>Construction of a Freshman Baseball Field at La Grande High School</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section section-alt">
  <div class="content-block">
    <h2>Hunt of a Lifetime</h2>
    <p>In 2012, G.R.A.Y. amended its bylaws to become a recognized sponsor for the Oregon Department of Fish and Wildlife's Hunt of a Lifetime program. This program provides hunting opportunities for terminally ill youth, offering them the chance to pursue deer, elk, or antelope without entering competitive tag drawings.</p>
    <p><a href="{{ '/hunt-of-a-lifetime/' | url }}" class="btn btn-accent">Learn More About This Program</a></p>
  </div>
</section>

